deliberate mistakes and a few words of Spanish. They represent a form of
clowning, an extension into the domain of the private letter of the polyglot
comedy, the commedia dell’arteWixh which Lasso was associated at the court.
Like a sophisticated Salvatore, Lasso mixes languages within sentences and
occasionally within a single word, as in the case of a term of his invention,
tregrandissamente.
